id: pmc-nagj
title: changelog --format json emits TOON on stdout without global --json
description: "pm-extension 'changelog generate --format json' and 'changelog export --format json' returned a structured object rendered as TOON on stdout; valid JSON required global --json. Fix: renderedCommandResult marker + toon/json renderer overrides so json-mode prints verbatim JSON; non-json returns fall through unchanged; default md byte-identical."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 3
tags[1]: bug
created_at: "2026-07-14T08:18:05.765Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-14T08:18:41.774Z"
closed_at: "2026-07-14T08:18:41.771Z"
author: claude-opus
acceptance_criteria: generate/export --format json emit valid JSON on stdout without --json; default md byte-identical; no new test failures.
resolution: Added renderedCommandResult marker + toon/json renderer overrides (renderers capability); wrapped generate/export json-mode returns.
expected_result: changelog generate/export --format json emit valid JSON on stdout without global --json
actual_result: "Verified: both emit valid JSON on stdout; default md byte-identical; 139 tests pass (2 pre-existing --isolated CLI-version failures unrelated)"
